Title: 099: How a Software Developer Re-Focused his life to Learn Artificial Intelligence
Description:
In this episode of the SuperDataScience Podcast, I chat with AI Learner, Tuatini Godard. You will get to explore the world of Deep Learning and AI, you will learn the role of games in AI development, and about the appropriate hardware for Deep Learning.
